        "detailedDescription_md": "The &amp;quot;Passenger Auto Rickshaw Loan Scheme&amp;quot; introduced by the Social Justice and Empowerment Department, Gujarat, aims to provide financial assistance in the form of loans to Scheduled Caste individuals from Antyodaya families to purchase passenger auto rickshaws, enabling them to generate sustainable income through transport services. The scheme is being implemented by the Dr. Ambedkar Antyodaya Development Corporation.\n",
